name: Foothills of Hell V.2 for Doom2 LEVEL 2
description: If you lived passed Level 1 you may not want to put your butt on the line once again. This Foot Hill of hell maybe your last. Beware of the REVNANT! He smells you when you enter. Most important don't stop moving! YOU WILL HATE ME! LEVEL 3 is forming even deeper in the THE FOOT HILLS OF HELL.
